      "raw": "Education\nPhD\n(From University of Kalyani, India under Commonwealth S/F ship Plan: 1993, Thesis submitted in 1996 and Degree awarded in 1999.)\nM.Com. (Accounting)\n(In 1983 from University of Chittagong and stood 1st Class 1st: University First.)\nB.Com. (Hons.)\n(In 1982 from University of Chittagong and stood 1st Class 1st: University First.)\nHSC\n(In 1979 from Government College of Commerce, Chittagong under Comilla Board and secured 1st Division 3rd Position in the merit list.)\nSSC\n(In 1977 from Suchiya Ram Krishna High School under Comilla Board and secured 1st Division 10th Position in the merit list.)"
